title: Bug 116564 - The title of the hyperlink builder should be 'Hyperlink Options', but it changes with settings.
OB: When I click on 'OK' and then reopen the hyperlink builder, the title of the hyperlink builder changes to 'www.actuate.com'.
EB: The expected behavior is that the title of the hyperlink builder should be 'Hyperlink Options'.
SR: To reproduce the issue: 1. Set a label hyperlink as 'www.actuate.com'. 2. Click on 'OK'. 3. Reopen the hyperlink builder.
